data.actual_result: It's already filled with some emojis, so it's actually impossible to have a clean frequently used emojis section
data.short_description: There are still frequently used emojis even after fresh install / data wipe of Discord
data.steps_to_repro: - Either uninstall/reinstall Discord or go in app manager > Discord > wipe data - Open Discord, login, and look at your frequently used emojis
